     Uncomment ballast so can be altered
     Add 'camber'        to Hstab, Vstab @, defult value 1.0 
     Add 'effectiveness' to Hstab, Vstab @, defult value 1.0 
     Add 'idrag'         to Hstab, Vstab @, defult value 1.0 
     Approch Speed = 80
     Wing        Stall Aoa = 15.0 ( 2deg margin ) Stall Width = 8.0 ( buckaroo )
